Hi <@UGASVFGF2> - Great to have you here!
> - What specific challenges are you finding yourself running into?
> - What specific questions do you have?


Make sure to check out the below two resources (I know you saw the academy course already) for help on best practices and getting going on the CMS. :slightly_smiling_face:

<https://designers.HubSpot.com/discoverykit>
<https://academy.HubSpot.com/courses/cms-for-developers>

Lastly, I'd recommend downloading some free templates from the Template Marketplace to see how they are structured. Then try to rebuild them from scratch and see if you can get them to match exactly.
